The Anambra state police command has arrested a Pastor for allegedly defiling a twelve years old girl in Awka. The said pastor, Mr Onyekwelu who is also a Lecturer at the Nnamdi Azikiwe University Awka was said to have been defiling the minor who had been living with him since Saturday last week. The minor who gave her name as Uju Okafor from Ufuma in Orumba North Local government areas of Anambra State, said that when she could not bear the pains of rape at about 9:30 pm on Wednesday jumped down from a two-storey building and broke her leg in the process. Narrating her ordeal to while receiving treatment at the Chukwuemeka Odumegwu Ojukwu University Teaching hospital in Awka, Uju said ‚Äù On Saturday my mother sent me to one woman who later took me to the house of Rev Onyekwelu for me to be cooking and cleaning the house for him since his family is not around.